---
import Card from '../Card.astro'
---

<Card
  colSpan="lg:col-span-1"
  rowSpan="lg:row-span-2"
  rowStart="lg:row-start-7"
  title="Goals"
>
  <div class="text-xm flex h-full w-full flex-col">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        I want to keep growing in backend architecture with a stronger focus on:
      </p>
      <ul class="tech-list list-inside list-disc text-xs">
        <strong class="goal-list">🧑‍💻 Microservices</strong>
        <p>
          Designing scalable and maintainable distributed systems with clear
          boundaries and reliable communication.
        </p>
        <strong class="goal-list">🧑‍💻 gRPC</strong>
        <p>
          Building faster and more efficient service-to-service communication
          for modern backend environments.
        </p>
        <strong class="goal-list">🧑‍💻 AI</strong>
        <p>
          Exploring practical ways to integrate AI into real products and
          backend workflows.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>
